1
00:01:17,200 --> 00:01:18,840
Lingyue of Gushan

2
00:01:19,160 --> 00:01:21,880
is the greatest Divine Physician of this generation.

3
00:01:21,880 --> 00:01:23,600
Didn't they say Divine Physician Lingyue

4
00:01:23,600 --> 00:01:25,320
retired to the mountains with her disciple long ago?

5
00:01:25,320 --> 00:01:26,280
Many years ago,

6
00:01:26,280 --> 00:01:28,000
Divine Physician Lingyue saved my life.

7
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:28,600
At that time,

8
00:01:28,600 --> 00:01:30,960
she seemed to have two little children with her.

9
00:01:30,960 --> 00:01:32,840
Even if you are the Gushan Divine Physician's disciple,

10
00:01:32,840 --> 00:01:33,759
you are not her.

11
00:01:33,840 --> 00:01:35,170
Who do you think you are?

12
00:01:35,240 --> 00:01:36,479
In terms of medical skills,

13
00:01:36,479 --> 00:01:37,880
if my master is first,

14
00:01:37,880 --> 00:01:39,280
I deserve to be second.

15
00:01:40,039 --> 00:01:41,120
Ridiculous.

16
00:01:41,680 --> 00:01:43,120
You are just a silly little girl.

17
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:45,360
How dare you compare yourself to the Divine Physician?

18
00:01:45,360 --> 00:01:46,890
It is simply preposterous.

19
00:01:47,080 --> 00:01:48,880
What's wrong with being a little girl?

20
00:01:48,880 --> 00:01:50,280
Don't find out later that your medical skills

21
00:01:50,280 --> 00:01:52,009
are worse than a little girl's,

22
00:01:52,080 --> 00:01:53,080
and start crying.

23
00:01:57,560 --> 00:02:00,480
You two, my skills are limited.

24
00:02:01,160 --> 00:02:02,320
As for Boss Hu's illness,

25
00:02:02,320 --> 00:02:04,120
we can do nothing to help.

26
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:05,960
You should seek help elsewhere.

27
00:02:05,960 --> 00:02:08,759
Desperate diseases must have desperate remedies.

28
00:02:08,759 --> 00:02:10,039
You'd rather kick the patient out

29
00:02:10,039 --> 00:02:11,640
than let us try.

30
00:02:12,200 --> 00:02:14,960
Are you afraid of ruining your reputation

31
00:02:15,480 --> 00:02:16,240
and losing face?

32
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:17,120
You...

33
00:02:17,320 --> 00:02:18,600
As a doctor,

34
00:02:18,760 --> 00:02:19,640
just for the sake of reputation,

35
00:02:19,640 --> 00:02:21,720
would you ignore a patient's life?

36
00:02:22,680 --> 00:02:24,040
How I handle things

37
00:02:24,040 --> 00:02:26,170
is none of your business, little girl.

38
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:29,200
Master!

39
00:02:29,560 --> 00:02:30,680
Master!

40
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:34,360
Master!

41
00:02:36,079 --> 00:02:37,810
Zhou, why are you so flustered?

42
00:02:37,920 --> 00:02:38,680
Master,

43
00:02:39,040 --> 00:02:41,480
the apprentice of the Gushan Divine Physician has arrived in town.

44
00:02:41,480 --> 00:02:45,040
Judging by her age, she is the little girl who followed the Divine Physician back then.

45
00:02:45,040 --> 00:02:45,840
Is that true?

46
00:02:49,079 --> 00:02:51,440
But after so many years,

47
00:02:51,440 --> 00:02:53,760
I'm afraid she won't remember what happened back then.

48
00:02:53,760 --> 00:02:55,360
We have to try.

49
00:02:55,880 --> 00:02:58,600
Since the Gushan Divine Physician saved Madam back then,

50
00:02:58,600 --> 00:03:01,930
that little girl must know the Young Master's whereabouts.

51
00:03:10,160 --> 00:03:10,960
You...

52
00:03:17,040 --> 00:03:18,800
Fine.

53
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:20,520
Since you want to show off,

54
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:21,880
I won't stop you.

55
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:25,560
But let me make this clear.

56
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:29,520
You two have nothing to do with my Du Family Medical Hall.

57
00:03:29,680 --> 00:03:31,920
If anything goes wrong,

58
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:35,000
you will be held solely responsible.

59
00:03:35,320 --> 00:03:36,850
Everyone here is a witness.

60
00:03:39,079 --> 00:03:40,640
That's not right.

61
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:41,880
If she fails,

62
00:03:41,880 --> 00:03:43,160
we'll take full responsibility.

63
00:03:43,160 --> 00:03:44,680
But if she succeeds,

64
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:48,640
the Director must kowtow and apologize to Doctor Ji.

65
00:03:58,079 --> 00:03:58,840
Deal.

66
00:03:59,280 --> 00:04:00,000
Today,

67
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:02,480
I'll play along with you two arrogant brats

68
00:04:02,480 --> 00:04:03,560
and take this bet.

69
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:07,440
Can this girl do it?

70
00:04:09,200 --> 00:04:10,560
Who knows?

71
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:13,690
By the looks of it, they might actually have some skills.

72
00:04:20,959 --> 00:04:21,760
Brother.

73
00:04:22,200 --> 00:04:23,000
Second Uncle,

74
00:04:23,120 --> 00:04:24,080
I trust them.

75
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:25,440
Let them try.

76
00:04:33,880 --> 00:04:34,800
Can you treat him or not?

77
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:36,730
Look how much pain my brother is in.

78
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:42,040
If you disturb her again,

79
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:43,040
I won't be polite.

80
00:04:43,080 --> 00:04:43,800
You...

81
00:04:44,240 --> 00:04:47,680
Second Uncle, I trust this gentleman and this young lady.

82
00:05:03,440 --> 00:05:04,360
Brother.

83
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:05,620
You're finally awake.

84
00:05:05,760 --> 00:05:06,690
I thought you...

85
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:09,800
Brother.

86
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:15,960
If he's really awake, won't Master Du...

87
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:18,240
Don't talk nonsense.

88
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:22,920
He really is awake.

89
00:05:24,440 --> 00:05:25,600
Brother.

90
00:05:26,880 --> 00:05:29,320
What happened to me?

91
00:05:38,320 --> 00:05:41,250
You're the ones who told me to see a doctor yesterday.

92
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:45,159
We...

93
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:50,800
Just as I thought.

94
00:05:51,280 --> 00:05:52,480
He's been poisoned.

95
00:05:55,880 --> 00:05:58,280
Who would want to kill my father?

96
00:06:02,400 --> 00:06:03,080
Boss Du.

97
00:06:03,080 --> 00:06:04,480
You must have poisoned the medicine.

98
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:05,280
Didn't you?

99
00:06:05,440 --> 00:06:06,120
You...

100
00:06:06,120 --> 00:06:07,440
You're talking nonsense.

101
00:06:07,440 --> 00:06:08,760
I'm talking nonsense?

102
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:11,200
You must want Big Brother to get worse

103
00:06:11,200 --> 00:06:12,360
so you can charge more money.

104
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:13,360
Isn't that right?

105
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:15,440
You're slandering me!

106
00:06:15,880 --> 00:06:17,120
Do you have any proof?

107
00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:17,800
You...

108
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:22,680
Dad, how are you feeling?

109
00:06:23,560 --> 00:06:24,240
Brother.

110
00:06:31,640 --> 00:06:32,600
Boss Hu.

111
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:34,320
Can you recall

112
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:36,800
when your symptoms worsened?

113
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:44,000
I remember now.

114
00:06:44,760 --> 00:06:48,720
After taking the medicine yesterday, I felt a bit off.

115
00:06:49,320 --> 00:06:50,880
I didn't think much of it,

116
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:54,360
thinking I was just having a relapse.

117
00:06:54,360 --> 00:06:57,840
But after taking the medicine today,

118
00:06:58,560 --> 00:07:00,320
I blacked out completely.

119
00:07:03,840 --> 00:07:04,720
Listen.

120
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:05,920
My big brother said

121
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:08,080
there must be something wrong here.

122
00:07:08,080 --> 00:07:08,880
Boss Du,

123
00:07:08,880 --> 00:07:11,360
it's bad enough that your medicine is so expensive.

124
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:12,440
But now,

125
00:07:12,440 --> 00:07:13,880
you're actually trying to kill for money.

126
00:07:13,880 --> 00:07:16,040
I think your heart is getting blacker and blacker.

127
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:16,800
This...

128
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:18,570
This is simply ridiculous.

129
00:07:18,640 --> 00:07:21,240
How could I, for such petty profits,

130
00:07:21,240 --> 00:07:23,280
ruin my own reputation?

131
00:07:23,480 --> 00:07:24,280
Besides,

132
00:07:24,360 --> 00:07:26,840
the Du family runs the only clinic in town.

133
00:07:26,880 --> 00:07:28,610
I have no need to cause trouble.

134
00:07:29,600 --> 00:07:34,760
Moreover, we all bought the medicine together that day.

135
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:38,880
Many people bought the same herbs.

136
00:07:38,880 --> 00:07:40,360
That's right.

137
00:07:42,080 --> 00:07:46,000
Medicine goes through several processes before reaching the patient.

138
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:48,840
Maybe the medical hall itself is fine.

139
00:07:49,440 --> 00:07:51,720
But if someone tampered with it,

140
00:07:52,080 --> 00:07:53,440
who knows?

141
00:07:54,440 --> 00:07:55,370
What do you mean?

142
00:07:55,520 --> 00:07:57,400
You think I'd hurt my own brother?

143
00:07:57,640 --> 00:08:00,080
Relax, we're just speculating.

144
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:01,680
Don't give yourself away.

145
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:02,400
You...

146
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:09,080
Um...

147
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:11,000
Quiet down, everyone.

148
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:11,880
Alright.

149
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:14,120
Boss Hu has woken up.

150
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:15,840
He needs to rest now.

151
00:08:16,280 --> 00:08:20,160
We can discuss everything else later.

152
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:22,080
Someone!

153
00:08:23,720 --> 00:08:25,780
Take Boss Hu to the guest room to rest.

154
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:41,039
I am truly sorry.

155
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:43,289
My second uncle has a quick temper.

156
00:08:43,400 --> 00:08:44,720
If he has offended you,

157
00:08:44,800 --> 00:08:46,040
please forgive him.

158
00:08:47,600 --> 00:08:50,260
I sincerely thank you both for saving my father.

159
00:08:50,560 --> 00:08:51,840
If there is a chance in the future,

160
00:08:51,840 --> 00:08:53,880
I will definitely repay you.

161
00:08:55,720 --> 00:08:56,960
Thank you, Doctor Ji.

162
00:08:57,120 --> 00:09:00,480
And thank you, Young Master, for helping treat my father.

163
00:09:01,080 --> 00:09:02,480
I didn't do anything.

164
00:09:02,760 --> 00:09:04,220
It was all thanks to Ji Bai.

165
00:09:05,640 --> 00:09:06,960
You are too polite, Miss Hu.

166
00:09:06,960 --> 00:09:08,720
This is my duty as a healer.

167
00:09:08,880 --> 00:09:10,810
There is no need for such courtesy.

168
00:09:11,640 --> 00:09:12,840
Xin'er, what are you doing?

169
00:09:12,840 --> 00:09:14,040
Hurry up and let's go.

170
00:09:23,720 --> 00:09:25,560
She's interested in you.

171
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:33,880
She likes me.

172
00:09:38,680 --> 00:09:40,610
Why are you looking at me like that?

173
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:41,720
Everyone,

174
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:43,640
Everyone, please calm down.

175
00:09:43,840 --> 00:09:45,160
Boss Hu is awake.

176
00:09:45,160 --> 00:09:47,040
The cause of the illness is clear.

177
00:09:47,040 --> 00:09:49,240
I will do my best to treat him.

178
00:09:49,240 --> 00:09:52,170
Everyone, please disperse if there is nothing else.

179
00:09:54,080 --> 00:09:57,600
Director Du, accept your loss.

180
00:09:57,600 --> 00:10:00,330
Shouldn't you kowtow and apologize to Doctor Ji?

181
00:10:03,240 --> 00:10:05,880
What? Trying to back out?

182
00:10:07,400 --> 00:10:09,480
What are you talking about?

183
00:10:10,040 --> 00:10:12,440
I didn't notice what was going on over here.

184
00:10:12,440 --> 00:10:14,280
Director Du just said,

185
00:10:15,040 --> 00:10:16,520
if we saved the patient,

186
00:10:16,520 --> 00:10:18,580
he would kowtow and apologize to you.

187
00:10:18,760 --> 00:10:22,160
Now he's dodging the issue.

188
00:10:22,640 --> 00:10:24,170
What is the meaning of this?

189
00:10:24,640 --> 00:10:27,480
Young man, don't push it too far.

190
00:10:27,760 --> 00:10:28,760
That's right.

191
00:10:28,760 --> 00:10:30,560
You should be lenient when possible.

192
00:10:30,560 --> 00:10:31,040
You...

193
00:10:33,880 --> 00:10:36,080
Well, things are clear now.

194
00:10:36,080 --> 00:10:37,360
Everyone, break it up.

195
00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:38,720
Move along.

196
00:10:39,560 --> 00:10:42,020
What are you looking at? Don't you have work?

197
00:10:42,320 --> 00:10:43,760
Move along.

198
00:10:51,920 --> 00:10:56,000
Doctor Ji, I was ignorant and short-sighted.

199
00:10:56,280 --> 00:10:58,080
I slighted you just now.

200
00:10:59,640 --> 00:11:02,480
Please accept my apology.

201
00:11:05,080 --> 00:11:07,280
If you need me in the future,

202
00:11:07,520 --> 00:11:09,280
just ask,

203
00:11:09,440 --> 00:11:11,440
and I will do my utmost to help.

204
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:13,480
No need to wait for the future.

205
00:11:13,480 --> 00:11:14,480
We have a

206
00:11:14,480 --> 00:11:16,800
sick friend who needs to stay for a few days.

207
00:11:16,800 --> 00:11:18,840
During this time, we might need

208
00:11:18,840 --> 00:11:21,000
your herbs and study.

209
00:11:25,160 --> 00:11:26,880
Consider it done.

210
00:11:26,960 --> 00:11:30,840
I happen to want to learn from you as well.

211
00:11:36,560 --> 00:11:37,690
Greetings, Father.

212
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:40,440
Did something happen here?

213
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:41,480
Is it resolved?

214
00:11:42,080 --> 00:11:43,080
You bastard.

215
00:11:43,480 --> 00:11:45,040
You idle around all day.

216
00:11:45,280 --> 00:11:47,080
What is the use of talking to you?

217
00:11:53,160 --> 00:11:55,040
Alright, let me introduce you.

218
00:11:55,520 --> 00:11:57,880
This is Divine Physician Ji and

219
00:11:58,520 --> 00:11:59,040
Shen Yi.

220
00:11:59,480 --> 00:12:00,960
We know Young Master Du.

221
00:12:02,080 --> 00:12:03,540
Since you know each other,

222
00:12:03,560 --> 00:12:05,600
I won't introduce you any further.

223
00:12:06,800 --> 00:12:10,080
These two will stay at our medical hall for a few days.

224
00:12:10,280 --> 00:12:12,040
Take them to get settled.

225
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:14,800
Yes. Please follow me, both of you.

226
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:17,240
Let's go.

227
00:12:28,600 --> 00:12:30,160
Master,

228
00:12:30,160 --> 00:12:32,160
are we really letting them stay here

229
00:12:32,160 --> 00:12:33,680
and freeload?

230
00:12:34,520 --> 00:12:35,760
What do you know?

231
00:12:36,320 --> 00:12:39,320
She is the disciple of the Divine Physician of Gushan.

232
00:12:39,600 --> 00:12:41,840
She showed her skills in public today.

233
00:12:42,600 --> 00:12:46,160
That will bring more customers to our medical hall.

234
00:12:47,280 --> 00:12:49,680
Even the Imperial Physicians in the palace

235
00:12:50,040 --> 00:12:52,880
might not match the Divine Physician's skills.

236
00:12:53,480 --> 00:12:54,400
By then,

237
00:12:54,560 --> 00:12:57,360
those dignitaries who looked down on us

238
00:12:57,360 --> 00:12:59,400
will come here for her fame.

239
00:12:59,680 --> 00:13:01,940
Once this golden signboard is polished,

240
00:13:02,880 --> 00:13:06,600
patients from the neighboring town will come too.

241
00:13:08,160 --> 00:13:09,680
In this way,

242
00:13:10,160 --> 00:13:11,920
the money they earn for us

243
00:13:12,080 --> 00:13:15,600
will far exceed the cost of their stay.

244
00:13:17,640 --> 00:13:19,360
As expected of the Master.

245
00:13:19,720 --> 00:13:22,240
You really are calculating.

246
00:13:23,040 --> 00:13:24,000
Get back to work.

247
00:14:03,400 --> 00:14:06,680
Wu, Zhang, Li, Zheng, Chen, Luo, Deng.

248
00:14:03,400 --> 00:14:04,720
Yi Yinan.

249
00:14:04,720 --> 00:14:06,680
Xiao Xiaoxue. Yi Yinan.

250
00:14:32,560 --> 00:14:33,680
Ma, Miao, Lu, Ran.

251
00:14:33,760 --> 00:14:34,760
Ma, Miao, Lu, Ran.

252
00:14:38,200 --> 00:14:39,800
Lyu, Sun, Zhang, Meng.

253
00:14:38,200 --> 00:14:39,800
Xiulong.

254
00:14:39,800 --> 00:14:40,360
Lyu, Sun, Zhang.
